SIMPLE: headstrong
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Headstrong
<hw>Head"strong`</hw> <pr>(-str⟦ocr⟧ng`; 115)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>Not easily restrained; ungovernable; obstinate;
stubborn.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Now let the <qex>headstrong</qex> boy my will control.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Directed by ungovernable will, or proceeding from
obstinacy; <as>as, a <ex>headstrong</ex> course</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Dryden.</au></rj></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Violent; obstinate; ungovernable; untractable;
stubborn; unruly; venturesome; heady.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Headstrongness</ent>⟦br⟧
